summary: 'Art of Captain Marvel' Cover Art Revealed
title: 'Art of Captain Marvel' Cover Art Revealed
body:
Every MCU movie receives a nice “Art of” book to go along with it, and now the cover for the upcoming “Marvel’s Captain Marvel: The Art of the Movie” has been released online. The art was being shared on social media this morning, but it was clear it was work by Andy Park. After he saw it was out, he made a Tweet about the cover, which you can see below.

My cover to The Art of Captain Marvel…
